This paper is about recommender systems, which are commonly studied in the sub-fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes algorithms for training the recommender, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of granular association rules suggests a focus on fuzzy logic and reasoning, which is a topic studied in the sub-field of soft computing (cs.SI). Finally, the paper involves data analysis and mining, which is a topic studied in the sub-field of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
